2
00:00:01.560 --> 00:00:03.730
Wealth, fame, power...

3
00:00:03.730 --> 00:00:07.990
Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
obtained everything the world has to offer.

4
00:00:07.990 --> 00:00:11.700
What he said in his final moments
drove countless souls to the seas.

5
00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:13.740
You want my treasure?

6
00:00:13.740 --> 00:00:15.580
Go ahead.

7
00:00:15.580 --> 00:00:16.830
Find it!

8
00:00:16.830 --> 00:00:19.460
Everything is right where I left it!

9
00:00:21.750 --> 00:00:26.550
People set their sights on the Grand Line
in pursuit of their dreams.

10
00:00:26.550 --> 00:00:29.680
The world has truly entered
the Great Pirate Era!

11
00:01:51.010 --> 00:01:54.180
"Oden's Travel Record"

12
00:01:51.800 --> 00:01:52.930
D?

13
00:01:56.430 --> 00:02:00.680
I never thought I'd be able to meet you!

14
00:02:01.140 --> 00:02:03.390
"O-Oden"...

15
00:02:04.020 --> 00:02:06.020
Is that my father's journal?!

16
00:02:06.060 --> 00:02:12.610
<b>Straw Hat Luffy</b>

17
00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:12.610
It contains every detail about his grand life
and the world he experienced!

18
00:02:13.740 --> 00:02:17.580
On that day, I found it at
the river below Oden Castle.

19
00:02:17.580 --> 00:02:21.160
Someone in the castle
must have kept it from burning...

20
00:02:21.160 --> 00:02:22.790
Lord Oden's...

21
00:02:24.420 --> 00:02:25.750
Momonosuke!

22
00:02:26.880 --> 00:02:30.710
He wrote a lot about you as well.

23
00:02:32.760 --> 00:02:35.640
You were born on Whitebeard's ship, right?!

24
00:02:35.970 --> 00:02:37.760
And then you went on to Roger's ship!

25
00:02:39.010 --> 00:02:40.310
Mm-hmm.

26
00:02:40.930 --> 00:02:47.230
Th-Though, since I was so young,
I do not remember much...

27
00:02:47.230 --> 00:02:49.940
Whitebeard, Roger, and Oden...

28
00:02:52.070 --> 00:02:53.280
They all said...

29
00:02:53.280 --> 00:02:53.320
They all said...

30
00:02:53.320 --> 00:02:53.400
They all said...

31
00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:53.440
They all said...

32
00:02:53.440 --> 00:02:53.490
They all said...

33
00:02:57.120 --> 00:02:59.370
that twenty years in the future,

34
00:03:02.250 --> 00:03:06.540
the New World was sure to be overrun
by young and powerful pirates!

35
00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:09.340
That future is now!

36
00:03:12.920 --> 00:03:16.880
I was sure that Ace would be
among them, leading the pack...

37
00:03:16.880 --> 00:03:22.560
But when he died, I remembered
something from that night!

38
00:03:25.560 --> 00:03:26.190
What...?

39
00:03:28.770 --> 00:03:30.150
Crap!

40
00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:31.730
I let it slip!

41
00:03:31.730 --> 00:03:34.440
I wasn't supposed to say that!

42
00:03:34.440 --> 00:03:36.150
You didn't hear that! Forget about it!

43
00:03:36.700 --> 00:03:38.700
And don't you dare laugh either!

44
00:03:38.700 --> 00:03:40.780
Sabo and I won't stand for it!

45
00:03:43.490 --> 00:03:45.330
That's at the end...

46
00:03:45.710 --> 00:03:47.330
of my kid brother's dream.

47
00:03:49.880 --> 00:03:54.760
Sure, we laughed when Luffy
told us, but that's okay!

48
00:03:54.760 --> 00:03:58.130
We're the only ones
who are allowed to laugh...

49
00:03:58.130 --> 00:03:59.760
'cause we believe in him!

50
00:03:59.760 --> 00:04:03.510
We really think he can do it, so–

51
00:04:03.510 --> 00:04:04.520
Ace!

52
00:04:06.390 --> 00:04:07.140
Huh?

53
00:04:08.020 --> 00:04:09.150
Hey!

54
00:04:09.150 --> 00:04:10.650
What's wrong, Yamato?

55
00:04:13.520 --> 00:04:16.360
I won't laugh!

56
00:04:17.240 --> 00:04:20.950
Those were the Pirate King's exact words!

57
00:04:20.950 --> 00:04:23.740
The very words that stunned Oden!

58
00:04:24.740 --> 00:04:29.960
In Kozuki Oden's journal, there was
a great man who said the same thing!

59
00:04:29.960 --> 00:04:31.580
I'd never laugh at that!

60
00:04:31.580 --> 00:04:33.590
Your brother is incredible!

61
00:04:35.460 --> 00:04:37.090
A great man, huh?

62
00:04:37.090 --> 00:04:38.590
Good to hear!

63
00:04:38.590 --> 00:04:42.050
Maybe Luffy and I can grab
a drink with him someday!

64
00:04:43.220 --> 00:04:45.260
I'm sure you guys would get along!

65
00:04:45.970 --> 00:04:47.230
But he's already dead.

66
00:04:47.230 --> 00:04:48.310
He is?!

67
00:04:49.850 --> 00:04:53.150
Well, in that case, it'd be hard to see him...

68
00:05:00.660 --> 00:05:01.410
It's done!

69
00:05:01.410 --> 00:05:02.070
Oh?

70
00:05:02.070 --> 00:05:04.030
This is your vivre card!

71
00:05:05.030 --> 00:05:06.790
This is it?

72
00:05:08.540 --> 00:05:10.120
It's just some paper.

73
00:05:10.750 --> 00:05:15.920
Yeah! But this piece of paper will
bring us together again one day!

74
00:05:17.260 --> 00:05:22.090
Give a piece to anyone you want
to keep track of or meet again.

75
00:05:22.760 --> 00:05:23.640
Okay!

76
00:05:23.640 --> 00:05:25.510
I'll be sure to do that.

77
00:05:45.370 --> 00:05:48.040
Ace!

78
00:05:55.540 --> 00:05:57.210
Yamato?!

79
00:06:01.590 --> 00:06:03.680
We will meet again one day!

80
00:06:04.050 --> 00:06:06.640
Ace!

81
00:06:14.270 --> 00:06:16.270
You bet!

82
00:06:23.150 --> 00:06:24.160
In reality...

83
00:06:25.070 --> 00:06:27.120
that would be our final meeting.

84
00:06:35.420 --> 00:06:40.800
I had no idea what was happening
in the outside world that day,

85
00:06:41.420 --> 00:06:44.260
but I read about it in the newspaper later.

86
00:06:44.760 --> 00:06:49.390
I learned that Ace was the son of
the Pirate King, Gol D. Roger...

87
00:06:50.140 --> 00:06:54.850
and that his younger brother
had really made a name for himself!

88
00:06:55.520 --> 00:06:57.310
That was the man you brought...

89
00:06:58.650 --> 00:06:59.520
Luffy!

90
00:07:01.780 --> 00:07:03.150
Momonosuke.

91
00:07:03.610 --> 00:07:06.570
I return this to you, of course.

92
00:07:06.570 --> 00:07:10.660
This is what Oden wrote about the future...

93
00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:23.760
Twenty years from now,

94
00:07:28.050 --> 00:07:35.100
a group of young and powerful pirates
shall start a new era in the New World!

95
00:07:36.730 --> 00:07:39.110
If I die before then...

96
00:07:39.110 --> 00:07:39.230
If I die before then...

97
00:07:39.230 --> 00:07:39.310
If I die before then...

98
00:07:43.230 --> 00:07:45.990
they will be the ones...

99
00:07:47.660 --> 00:07:49.620
to strike down Kaido!

100
00:07:50.240 --> 00:07:52.240
And here's another one...

101
00:07:52.240 --> 00:07:54.500
How about you sit back
and watch how it's done?!

102
00:07:54.500 --> 00:07:55.710
I refuse!

103
00:07:55.000 --> 00:07:55.710
Same here!

104
00:07:56.370 --> 00:07:58.670
So many heads ripe for the taking!

105
00:08:01.250 --> 00:08:03.380
Straw Hat...

106
00:08:20.310 --> 00:08:21.560
Linlin!

107
00:08:21.560 --> 00:08:25.320
You wanna guess what this brat
said he'd be, right to my face?!

108
00:08:25.320 --> 00:08:27.820
He sure is a cheeky one...

109
00:08:28.240 --> 00:08:31.820
He talked a big game to me too!

110
00:08:31.820 --> 00:08:35.450
He even destroyed my castle!

111
00:08:35.450 --> 00:08:38.960
I believe you owe me an apology, Straw Hat!

112
00:08:43.840 --> 00:08:45.380
Hey, punk...

113
00:08:45.840 --> 00:08:49.680
Tell us again what you said you'll be...

114
00:08:49.680 --> 00:08:54.600
Say it to right our faces!

115
00:09:05.150 --> 00:09:07.740
You alright, Kin'emon?

116
00:09:08.860 --> 00:09:11.160
I'm sorry...

117
00:09:12.200 --> 00:09:13.740
I took too long.

118
00:09:21.210 --> 00:09:23.630
I am... chagrined...

119
00:09:26.920 --> 00:09:28.880
A-Alas...

120
00:09:29.420 --> 00:09:31.220
when I pass on...

121
00:09:31.760 --> 00:09:35.930
I will have nothing to show
Lord Oden but my shame!

122
00:09:37.310 --> 00:09:38.140
Kin'e–

123
00:09:40.480 --> 00:09:43.350
Would you carry...

124
00:09:44.730 --> 00:09:47.150
Wano upon your back?!

125
00:09:49.400 --> 00:09:50.030
I beg–

126
00:09:50.030 --> 00:09:51.150
Dummy!

127
00:09:51.150 --> 00:09:52.700
Of course I will!

128
00:09:54.200 --> 00:09:55.990
It's my friends' country!

129
00:10:02.580 --> 00:10:04.830
Hey, brat!

130
00:10:07.090 --> 00:10:08.170
Sir...

131
00:10:08.800 --> 00:10:10.090
Luffy...

132
00:10:11.260 --> 00:10:13.340
We are all in...

133
00:10:13.340 --> 00:10:14.430
your debt...

134
00:10:16.180 --> 00:10:16.970
Traffy!

135
00:10:16.970 --> 00:10:19.390
Send all of them downstairs!

136
00:10:24.650 --> 00:10:27.110
Why is it shaking again?!

137
00:10:27.690 --> 00:10:29.110
Luffy...

138
00:10:32.570 --> 00:10:38.030
You call it haki, but in Wano
we refer to it as ryuo.

139
00:10:38.030 --> 00:10:40.910
It means "to flow."

140
00:10:40.910 --> 00:10:44.120
Lord Oden was executed!

141
00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:48.340
By the shogun of Wano and the pirate Kaido!

142
00:10:48.340 --> 00:10:48.380
By the shogun of Wano and the pirate Kaido!

